{"id": 1690, "genre": 1001, "title": "关于恋爱，你理想中的相遇方式是怎样的？", "description": "这种意外真是可以列在“艳遇指南之千载难逢天上掉馅饼”系列手册里。（题图来自：Tasso Art）", "record_count": 4566, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170516101240mUvV3W0z6nDPl2k4.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-05-18T03:00:21Z", "options": [{"id": 204800, "content": "同桌", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 52647}, {"id": 205056, "content": "梨花带雨", "image": "img/option/option/20170519024444vROTrNKgdl9CkU2M", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1035047}, {"id": 206080, "content": "相视而笑", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1037160}, {"id": 204801, "content": "一见钟情，就像相熟已久", "image": null, "praise_count": 25, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1034646}, {"id": 205057, "content": "就是先做朋友 然后自然而然的在一起 简简单单的", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1014928}, {"id": 206337, "content": "阳光很好，你比阳光更耀眼", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1037651}, {"id": 204802, "content": "日久生情", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 993137}, {"id": 208898, "content": "工作中接触到的合作伙伴", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1024616}, {"id": 204803, "content": "故事都是从一方先耍流氓开始的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1017698}, {"id": 207363, "content": "这么多年我终于明白了，世界上没有永久的婚姻，只有共同成长的夫妻", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1040300}, {"id": 210691, "content": "只因为在人海中多看了一眼", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1050042}, {"id": 204804, "content": "心照不宣的默契", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 535986}, {"id": 206084, "content": "不在相亲桌上", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1037129}, {"id": 204805, "content": "蓦然回首那人却在灯火阑珊处", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1290021}, {"id": 205061, "content": "偶然遇见多看一眼，然后总是遇见，最后两人相视一笑", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 163303}, {"id": 205062, "content": "看似交浅切莫言深，实则两人都想谈更多。", "image": "img/option/option/20170519043338sfRIYB8QEGkHgD7a.jpg", "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 746414}, {"id": 210182, "content": "恋爱？我选择孤独终老", "image": "img/option/option/20170606192514Be9lqdKktvw3Fg1u", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 855034}, {"id": 204807, "content": "互相扶持，互相成全", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 842303}, {"id": 206087, "content": "一见钟情", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1026743}, {"id": 204808, "content": "艳遇", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1023841}, {"id": 205576, "content": "所有的相遇都是久别重逢：）", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1036176}, {"id": 207112, "content": "在每年一次回老家的火车上，因为可以顺便带回家。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1039593}, {"id": 208648, "content": "互相帮助，成为朋友", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 897189}, {"id": 204809, "content": "青梅竹马or一见钟情", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1034655}, {"id": 205065, "content": "在风花雪月中那个一眼就消除疲惫的他", "image": "img/option/option/20170519055010M1h6A0SVU7K3CeEu.jpg", "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 579910}, {"id": 205321, "content": "不知道啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1033458}, {"id": 205833, "content": "日久生情", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1036445}, {"id": 205066, "content": "在一起可以做自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1017911}, {"id": 205322, "content": "遇见，合适了的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1035534}, {"id": 204811, "content": "幻想一定是像偶像剧里的那样，刚开始糟糕的相遇然后看对方各种不顺眼，然后到最后竟然彼此相爱。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1034660}, {"id": 205067, "content": "她", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1013842}, {"id": 206091, "content": "同个教室上课…", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1037179}, {"id": 204812, "content": "我好像在哪见过你", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1034663}, {"id": 205068, "content": "我喜欢的人也会喜欢我", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 672156}, {"id": 207372, "content": "分手后，估计就是相亲了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1040326}, {"id": 204813, "content": "在快崩溃时一个微小的帮助", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1034666}, {"id": 204814, "content": "认识在生活正常交往中   然后慢慢了解  双方父母都很喜欢", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1001167}, {"id": 205070, "content": "都有Ta .", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 977941}, {"id": 206094, "content": "漫展", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1036557}, {"id": 205071, "content": "互相包容 你对我的不满 我对你的不满可以互相交流", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 665800}, {"id": 204816, "content": "相互遇见，路过，回头，相视一笑", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 978978}, {"id": 204817, "content": "爱情太可怕了，不谈。", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1030711}, {"id": 205073, "content": "美术馆", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 395626}, {"id": 207121, "content": "她说了一句很走心的话，我就喜欢上啦。\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1039621}, {"id": 204818, "content": "我说错了那么多终于懂了可惜已经晚了，你说还没有。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 596101}, {"id": 205074, "content": "我喜欢你 你喜欢我 没有错过", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 890189}, {"id": 205330, "content": "我希望我们是从朋友开始发展的，从相识到相知。他知道我的缺点和死穴，我知道他的软肋和不足。相互包容，相互理解，就这样平平淡淡地过完这一生。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1035549}, {"id": 205586, "content": "能hold得住我就可以了 (然而至今没遇到", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1036228}, {"id": 204819, "content": "梦中一直追寻的背影，突然某天在路上碰到，拍拍肩，转过头……丑也认了……", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 935385}, {"id": 205075, "content": "从小在一起，一起走过人生", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 976303}]}